author: valsdav
body:
Models converted with the command, after installing tf2onnx in a CMSSW_16_0_0_pre4 release.

```
python3 -m tf2onnx.convert --output model.onnx --input model.pb --inputs FirstLayer_input:0 --outputs sequential/FinalLayer/Sigmoid:0 --opset 18
```
title: Convert PFID models from TF to ONNX
